        "# 🧬 Aviothic.ai: Basic Breast Cancer Training Notebook\n",
        "\n",
        "This is a baseline notebook for standard training. For the **Ensemble + YOLO + Multi-view** advanced features, please use **train_advanced.ipynb** instead."
      ]
